query: SELECT SUM(Submission_ID), Author, College FROM submission WHERE Author IN (SELECT Author FROM submission WHERE  Scores != 59) ORDER BY Author DESC

SELECT Venue, Date FROM workshop JOIN Acceptance ON Acceptance.Workshop_ID = workshop.Workshop_ID WHERE  Acceptance.Workshop_ID = 33 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Acceptance WHERE workshop.Workshop_ID = Workshop_ID)
SELECT MAX(Workshop_ID), Workshop_ID, Date, Venue FROM workshop WHERE Workshop_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Date > (SELECT SUM(Date) FROM workshop WHERE  Workshop_ID > 23) GROUP BY Venue

SELECT Date, Scores FROM submission JOIN workshop JOIN Acceptance ON Acceptance.Workshop_ID = workshop.Workshop_ID AND submission.Submission_ID = Acceptance.Submission_ID WHERE  workshop.Workshop_ID < 67 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM workshop AS s WHERE s.Workshop_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Acceptance.Submission_ID = s.Workshop_ID) GROUP BY Scores
SELECT m.Workshop_ID, m.Name FROM workshop AS m WHERE  m.Workshop_ID >= 39 LIMIT 3

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Date), Author FROM submission JOIN workshop JOIN Acceptance ON Acceptance.Workshop_ID = workshop.Workshop_ID AND submission.Submission_ID = Acceptance.Submission_ID WHERE  submission.Submission_ID = 33 GROUP BY Author ORDER BY Author DESC LIMIT 5

SELECT SUM(Workshop_ID), Name, Date FROM workshop WHERE  Workshop_ID != 81 GROUP BY Date

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT v.Author), v.Submission_ID FROM submission AS v WHERE  v.Scores >= 11

SELECT Submission_ID FROM Acceptance WHERE  Submission_ID = 66

SELECT Workshop_ID, Submission_ID FROM Acceptance WHERE  Workshop_ID >= 1 ORDER BY Workshop_ID DESC

SELECT s.Workshop_ID FROM Acceptance AS s WHERE s.Workshop_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  s.Workshop_ID >= 51 GROUP BY s.Workshop_ID HAVING SUM(s.Submission_ID) >= 46
